 3420    private async Task Cleanup(ChangeRequestOptions options, CancellationToken cancellationToken = default)
 03421    {
 03422        var dataKey = "<cleanup-data>";
 3423
 03424        if (migrationService.NeedMigration<RolePackage>(dataKey, 1))
 03425        {
 03426            await CleanupRolePackage(options, cancellationToken);
 03427            await migrationService.LogMigration<RolePackage>(dataKey, string.Empty, 1);
 03428        }
 3429
 03430        if (migrationService.NeedMigration<RolePackage>(dataKey, 2))
 03431        {
 03432            await CleanupNufRolePackage(options, cancellationToken);
 03433            await migrationService.LogMigration<RolePackage>(dataKey, "Delete non-nuf limited role connections to urn:al
 03434        }
 3435
 03436        if (migrationService.NeedMigration<Role>(dataKey, 1))
 03437        {
 03438            await CleanupAdminRoles(options, cancellationToken);
 03439            await migrationService.LogMigration<Role>(dataKey, "Delete old admin roles urn:altinn:role:klientadministrat
 03440        }
 03441    }

 3443    private async Task CleanupRolePackage(ChangeRequestOptions options, CancellationToken cancellationToken = default)
 03444    {
 03445        var packages = new Dictionary<string, Guid>();
 03446        foreach (var pack in await packageService.Get())
 03447        {
 03448            packages.Add(pack.Urn, pack.Id);
 03449        }
 3450
 03451        var roles = new Dictionary<string, Guid>();
 03452        foreach (var role in await roleService.Get())
 03453        {
 03454            roles.Add(role.Urn, role.Id);
 03455        }
 3456
 03457        var variants = new Dictionary<string, Guid>();
 03458        foreach (var variant in await entityVariantService.Get())
 03459        {
 03460            variants.Add(variant.Name, variant.Id);
 03461        }
 3462
 3463        try
 03464        {
 03465            var filter = rolePackageRepository.CreateFilterBuilder();
 03466            filter.Equal(t => t.RoleId, roles["urn:altinn:external-role:ccr:forretningsforer"]);
 03467            filter.Equal(t => t.PackageId, packages["urn:altinn:accesspackage:forretningsforer-eiendom"]);
 03468            filter.Equal(t => t.EntityVariantId, variants["BBL"]);
 03469            await rolePackageRepository.Delete(filter, options, cancellationToken: cancellationToken);
 03470        }
 03471        catch (Exception)
 03472        {
 03473        }
 03474    }
 3475
 3476    private async Task CleanupNufRolePackage(ChangeRequestOptions options, CancellationToken cancellationToken = default
 03477    {
 03478        var filter = rolePackageRepository.CreateFilterBuilder();
 03479        filter.Equal(t => t.RoleId, Guid.Parse("69c4397a-9e34-4e73-9f69-534bc1bb74c8")); // urn:altinn:external-role:ccr
 03480        filter.Equal(t => t.PackageId, Guid.Parse("5dad616e-5538-4e3f-b15a-bae33f06c99f")); // urn:altinn:accesspackage:
 03481        var nufRolePackages = await rolePackageRepository.Get(filter, cancellationToken: cancellationToken);
 3482
 03483        if (nufRolePackages.Any())
 03484        {
 03485            foreach (var rolePackage in nufRolePackages.Where(rp => rp.EntityVariantId == null))
 03486            {
 03487                await rolePackageRepository.Delete(rolePackage.Id, options, cancellationToken: cancellationToken);
 03488            }
 03489        }
 03490    }

 3492    private async Task CleanupAdminRoles(ChangeRequestOptions options, CancellationToken cancellationToken = default)
 03493    {
 03494        var filter = roleService.CreateFilterBuilder();
 03495        filter.In(t => t.Urn, ["urn:altinn:role:klientadministrator", "urn:altinn:role:tilgangsstyrer", "urn:altinn:role
